snippet.title: SpellRogue Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
SpellRogue is releasing into Early Access on February 12th!
Steam Page:   https://store.steampowered.com/app/1990110/SpellRogue/

SpellRogue is a turn-based, deckbuilding roguelike where you cast powerful spells using your Mana Dice, gain legendary artifacts, upgrade your spells and experiment with potent combinations to annihilate the Voidwalkers corrupting the world.


Learn more on our Socials:
Discord      -   https://discord.com/invite/5AnXVPCqyx
Twitter       -   https://twitter.com/Spellrogue
Webpage   -   https://www.spellrogue.com/

Music: Trailer by Alexander Nakarada (www.creatorchords.com)

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
